  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "It seems like we reject local transactions whose gas price is too low:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/hyperledger/besu/blob/2374f3b704ac24191b6e615c19057474041c4fad/ethereum/eth/src/main/java/org/hyperledger/besu/ethereum/eth/transactions/TransactionPool.java#L166\r\n\r\nAs far as I know, this is never desired behavior.\r\n\r\nAcceptance Criteria:\r\n* Come up with all scenarios under which a node operator would want local transactions rejected for having low gas prices.\r\n* See if any of them are compelling enough reasons to not do the following.\r\n* Change the method in the code snippet above to not reject the transaction.",
